Directed by: Lew Landers Actors: Production Company: Republic Pictures (I) Release Date: 11 September 1940 (USA) Aspect Ratio: 1.37 : 1 Woody Davis and are Tex Moore ambitious and enterprising friends who decide to become South American oil drillers in hope of becoming wealthy. Woody and Tex set up a site, but unfortunately, must spend their time fending off attacks from the rebellious locals. Their friendship is also threatened by the beautiful Havana who comes between them.
